<text top="1654" left="156" width="556" height="54" font="font11" id="p1_t26" reading_order_no="10" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">Software  Process  Change”  [2].</text>
<text top="1699" left="155" width="585" height="62" font="font8" id="p1_t27" reading_order_no="11" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">The  first  principle  was  “Start  at</text>
