<text top="2014" left="156" width="542" height="62" font="font8" id="p1_t33" reading_order_no="17" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">the  top  don’t  really  want  it,  it</text>
<text top="2066" left="155" width="609" height="62" font="font8" id="p1_t34" reading_order_no="18" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">won't  happen.  Many  of  us  in  the</text>
<text top="2118" left="156" width="607" height="62" font="font8" id="p1_t35" reading_order_no="19" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">business  of  software  can  point  to</text>
<text top="2171" left="157" width="543" height="61" font="font9" id="p1_t36" reading_order_no="20" segment_no="6" tag_type="text">initiatives  where  the  commit-</text>
