<text top="2479" left="831" width="287" height="63" font="font10" id="p1_t57" reading_order_no="56" segment_no="4" tag_type="text">ponent  was  cov-</text>
<text top="2539" left="831" width="398" height="55" font="font12" id="p1_t58" reading_order_no="57" segment_no="4" tag_type="text">ered  saying,  in  effect,  I</text>
